<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Auf der Homepage gibt es auch noch viele weitere Informationen, zum Beispiel zur Besucherstruktur und eine Liste der Aussteller.</p>
<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Die nächste Messe wird übrigens im Februar die <a href=\"http://www.didacta.de/\" target=\"_blank\">Didacta in Köln</a> sein.</p>
<p style=\"text-align:justify;\">Herzliche Grüße<br />
Christine</p><br />  <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/chkonstantinidis.wordpress.com/1668/\"><img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/chkonstantinidis.wordpress.com/1668/\" /></a> <img alt=\"\" border=\"0\" src=\"http://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=erfolgreichessprachenlernen.com&#038;blog=71912330&#038;post=1668&#038;subd=chkonstantinidis&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" />") (commentRss nil "http://erfolgreichessprachenlernen.com/2016/01/12/die-expolingua-2015-in-berlin-eine-nachlese/feed/") (comments nil "0") (content ((url . "http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/14040dba697651a8bb50c649030b4d1f?s=96&d=identicon&r=G") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "chkonstantinidis")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/expolingua.gif") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "Expolingua")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00746.jpg?w=113") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00746")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00779.jpg?w=150") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00779")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00774.jpg?w=150") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00774")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00745.jpg?w=150") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00745")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00770.jpg?w=150") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00770")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00769.jpg?w=113") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00769")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstantinidis.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/dsc00765.jpg?w=150") (medium . "image")) (title ((type . "html")) "DSC00765")) (content ((url . "https://chkonstant